<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>getfursu.it, but broke :(</title>

    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
          integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <style>
        iframe {
            border: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container p-5">
    <div class="jumbotron bg-light border-warning border">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <h1 class="display-4">Error 482{% if status_code >= 500 %}<sup>*</sup>{% endif %} ðŸ™€</h1>
            <p class="lead">Somebody shot the server with a 12-gauge. Please contact your administrator.</p>
            <hr class="my-4">
            <p class="text-danger">
                {% if status_code == 404 %}
                    No, but seriously, the page/resource you requested does not exist (404). Broken or outdated link? Typo in the address?
                {% elseif status_code == 410 %}
                    No, but seriously, the page/resource you requested is no longer served (410). Broken or outdated link? Typo in the address?
                {% else %}
                    No, but seriously, something went wrong. My apologies for the inconvenience!
                {% endif %}
            </p>
            <p class="mt-5 overflow-x-auto">
                <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/nxXrYOnFLEk?start=375"
                        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                        allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </p>

            {% if status_code != 404 %}
                <small>* 4xx errors are reserved for client-side errors, but whatever</small>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
